definitions.definition: A person who identifies as male , or animal already known or implied.
They ; he or she ( a person whose gender is unknown or irrelevant ) .
examples: The rulebook clearly states that "if any student is caught cheating, he will be expelled", and you were caught cheating, were you not, Anna?
definitions.label_groups: personal , sometimes proscribed , see usage notes

definitions.definition: It ; an animal whose gender is unknown.
A genderless object regarded as masculine, such as certain stars or planets (e.g. Sun, Mercury, Mars, Jupiter) or certain ships.
